  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed first floor rear extension by reason of the position, scale, and bulk would result in incongruous and out-of-keeping additions that fail to respect the character and appearance of the host dwellings and the wider terrace. As such the proposal is contrary to policies D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach) and D4 (Delivering good design) of the London Plan (2021) and policy LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020) and the guidance contained within Hackney&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed first floor rear extension by virtue of its height, depth and siting in relation to the neighbouring property at 6 St Andrews Grove would result in harm to the provision of daylight/sunlight to this neighbouring resident, contrary to Policy LP2 (Development and Amenity) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020), Policy D3 (Optimising Site Potential Through a Design Led Approach) and D14 (Noise) of the London Plan (2021) and the Residential Extensions and Alterations Supplementary Planning Document 2009&lt;/p&gt;"
